name: INCallRecordType
desc: Constants describing the type of the call.

items.name: case outgoing
items.desc: A call initiated by the current user.

items.name: case missed
items.desc: A received call that the user did not answer.

items.name: case received
items.desc: A received call that the user answered.

items.name: case latest
items.desc: The most recent call involving the user.

items.name: case voicemail
items.desc: A voicemail left from a missed call.

items.name: case inProgress
items.desc: A received call that is currently in progress.

items.name: case onHold
items.desc: A received call that the user has put on hold.

items.name: case ringing
items.desc: An incoming call that is currently causing the userâ€™s phone to ring.
